@DATABASE "Mikie"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - M - Mikie"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - M
                   ====================================

                                   Mikie
                                   =====



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(46259,255)"}               46259,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(40843,182)"}               40843,182

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
